                <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="winter-routes">
            <h3>Key Routes at Risk</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>A646 Cliviger Gorge</strong> &mdash; High altitude, exposed, frequent closures</li>
              <li><strong>A671 Deerplay Moor</strong> &mdash; Elevated moorland crossing to Bacup</li>
              <li><strong>Worsthorne / Hurstwood</strong> &mdash; Elevated villages, narrow roads</li>
              <li><strong>M65 J10-14</strong> &mdash; LCC-maintained section, exposed at higher elevation</li>
              <li><strong>Haggate / Briercliffe Road</strong> &mdash; Higher ground, steep gradients</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
